    <div class="content contentmobilhome">
        @await Html.PartialAsync("_HeaderEnglishMobile")
        <div class="textbodysecondtexten">
            <h4>Dermapen Microneedling Treatment</h4>
        </div>
           <div class="mainmainbox">
                
            <div class="mainbox">
                <div class="imgcavitspain">
                    <img src="~/images/dermapen.jpeg" width="50px" height="30px" class="imgdermmainpic" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    <h6>What Is Dermapen? </h6>
                    <p>
                        Dermapen is a cutting-edge microneedling device designed to improve the appearance of skin imperfections by creating thousands of micro-channels in the skin. These tiny, controlled punctures stimulate the body’s natural collagen and elastin production, triggering cellular renewal and delivering visible results with minimal downtime.
                        The Dermapen device features ultra-fine, vertically positioned needles that glide smoothly over the skin, making it precise, safe, and ideal for targeting even sensitive areas like around the eyes, lips, and nose.
                    </p>
                    <h6>What Can Dermapen Treat?</h6>
                    <p>
                        Dermapen is incredibly versatile and can effectively improve the appearance of:
                        ✅ Fine lines and wrinkles
                        ✅ Acne scarring and surgical scars
                        ✅ Stretch marks
                        ✅ Enlarged pores
                        ✅ Hyperpigmentation and melasma
                        ✅ Uneven skin tone and texture
                        ✅ Sun damage
                        ✅ Hair loss (alopecia), when used on the scalp
                        Whether you're looking for a youthful glow, smoother skin, or targeted scar reduction, Dermapen is a powerful, clinically proven solution.
                    </p>
                    <h6>Key Benefits of Dermapen</h6>
                    <p>
                        ✨ Stimulates Natural Collagen Production for long-term skin regeneration<br/>
                        ✨ Minimally Invasive with little to no downtime<br />
                        ✨Safe for All Skin Types including sensitive and darker tones<br />
                        ✨ Targets Delicate Areas like around the eyes and lips with precision<br />
                        ✨ Enhances Absorption of skincare products applied after treatment<br />
                        ✨ Customizable Treatments tailored to your unique skin needs<br />
                    </p>
                    <h6>What to Expect</h6>
                    <p>
                        ⚡Treatment Time: 30–60 minutes<br />
                        ⚡Downtime: Mild redness for 24–72 hours (similar to a light sunburn)<br />
                        ⚡Recommended Sessions: 3–6 treatments, spaced 4–6 weeks apart for optimal results<br />
                        ⚡Our expert clinicians will assess your skin, customize the treatment depth, and apply soothing serums for maximum comfort and results.<br />
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
